file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: Allows users to extract, create, update and configure IRN data.
  title: IRN API v1
  version: "1"
servers:
- description: Production Server
  url: https://api.factset.com/research/irn
- description: Sandbox
  url: https://api-sandbox.factset.com/research/irn
security:
- FactSetApiKey: []
- FactSetOAuth2: []
tags:
- name: CustomSymbols
- name: CustomSymbols - Relationships
- name: HybridSymbols
paths:
  /v1/custom-symbols:
    get:
      operationId: GetCustomSymbols
      parameters:
      - description: filter custom symbols based on custom symbol type
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: typeName
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: filter custom symbols based on custom symbol code or name
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: query
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Whether or not to include customFieldValues
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: includeCustomFieldValues
        required: false
        schema:
          default: false
          type: boolean
        style: form
      - description: Whether or not to exclude linked custom symbol
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: excludeLinkedCustomSymbol
        required: false
        schema:
          default: false
          type: boolean
        style: form
      - description: Whether or not to include event
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: includeEvent
        required: false
        schema:
          default: true
          type: boolean
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/CustomSymbolDto'
                type: array
          description: Success
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Get list of all custom symbols in your group along with some of their
        standard field and custom fields data
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-accepts: application/json
    post:
      operationId: CreateCustomSymbol
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolDto'
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolDto'
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolDto'
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolDto'
        description: createCustomSymbolDto object to save
      responses:
        "201":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NewItemDto'
          description: Created
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Create a custom symbol
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/{customSymbolId}:
    delete:
      operationId: DeleteCustomSymbol
      parameters:
      - description: customSymbolId to delete associated custom symbol
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: customSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Delete a custom symbol
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-accepts: application/json
    get:
      operationId: GetCustomSymbol
      parameters:
      - description: customSymbolId to get associated custom symbol
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: customSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Whether or not to include event
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: includeEvent
        required: false
        schema:
          default: false
          type: boolean
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CustomSymbolDto'
          description: Success
      summary: Get all custom field and standard field details on a specific custom
        symbol
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-accepts: application/json
    patch:
      operationId: PatchCustomSymbol
      parameters:
      - description: customSymbolId to update associated custom symbol
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: customSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          application/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          text/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
        description: updateCustomSymbolDto object to update
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Edit a custom symbol’s standard field and custom field data
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/{customSymbolId}/records:
    get:
      operationId: GetCustomSymbolRecords
      parameters:
      - description: CustomSymbolId to get associated records
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: customSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/RecordPreviewDto'
                type: array
          description: Success
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Get all notes and meetings where a specific customSymbol was tagged
        as primary or related identifier
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/standard-symbol-metadata/{standardSymbol}:
    get:
      operationId: GetStandardSymbolMetadataGuid
      parameters:
      - description: Standard symbol to get associated customSymbolId
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: standardSymbol
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                format: uuid
                type: string
          description: Success
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Get all custom field and standard field details on a specific standard
        symbol
      tags:
      - HybridSymbols
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/symbol-relationships/{symbolId}/relationships:
    get:
      operationId: GetSymbolRelationships
      parameters:
      - description: symbolId to get associated records
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: symbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipDto'
                type: array
          description: Success
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Returns a list of a symbol’s relationships
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols - Relationships
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/symbol-relationships/{symbolRelationshipId}:
    delete:
      operationId: DeleteSymbolRelationship
      parameters:
      - description: symbolRelationshipId to delete associated record
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: symbolRelationshipId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Delete a symbol relationship
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols - Relationships
      x-accepts: application/json
    get:
      operationId: GetSymbolRelationship
      parameters:
      - description: symbolRelationshipId to get associated record
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: symbolRelationshipId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipDto'
          description: Success
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Get details on a specific symbol relationship
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols - Relationships
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/{customSymbolId}/link-standard-symbol:
    post:
      operationId: LinkCustomSymbolToStandardSymbol
      parameters:
      - description: customSymbolId associated with custom symbol
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: customSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/StandardSymbolDto'
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/StandardSymbolDto'
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/StandardSymbolDto'
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/StandardSymbolDto'
        description: standard symbol name
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
      summary: Link custom symbol to standard symbol
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/standard-symbol-metadata:
    post:
      operationId: CreateStandardSymbolMetadata
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateStandardSymbolMetadataDto'
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateStandardSymbolMetadataDto'
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateStandardSymbolMetadataDto'
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateStandardSymbolMetadataDto'
        description: createStandardSymbolMetadataDto object to save
      responses:
        "201":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NewItemDto'
          description: Created
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Create standard symbol metadata
      tags:
      - HybridSymbols
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/symbol-relationships:
    post:
      operationId: CreateSymbolRelationship
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipSaveDto'
              type: array
          application/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipSaveDto'
              type: array
          text/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipSaveDto'
              type: array
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipSaveDto'
              type: array
        description: symbolRelationship object to save
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Created
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Create a symbol relationship
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols - Relationships
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/symbol-relationships/{symbol}:
    put:
      operationId: EditAndAddSymbolRelationship
      parameters:
      - explode: false
        in: path
        name: symbol
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipUpdateDto'
              type: array
          application/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipUpdateDto'
              type: array
          text/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipUpdateDto'
              type: array
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SymbolRelationshipUpdateDto'
              type: array
        description: symbolRelationship object to save
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
      summary: Edit a symbol relationship
      tags:
      - CustomSymbols - Relationships
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /v1/custom-symbols/standard-symbol-metadata/{standardSymbolId}:
    patch:
      operationId: PatchStandardSymbol
      parameters:
      - description: standardSymbolId to update associated standard symbol
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: standardSymbolId
        required: true
        schema:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          application/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          text/json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Operation'
              type: array
        description: updateCustomSymbolDto object to update
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
        "400":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Bad Request
        "404":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Not Found
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ProblemDetails'
          description: Error
      summary: Edit a standard symbol’s standard field and custom field data
      tags:
      - HybridSymbols
      x-contentType: application/json-patch+json
      x-accepts: application/json
components:
  schemas:
    CreateCustomSymbolCustomFieldValueDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        dateValue: dateValue
        code: code
        textValue: textValue
        numericValue: 0.8008281904610115
        extendedTextValue: extendedTextValue
        contactIds:
        - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        optionValues:
        - optionValues
        - optionValues
      properties:
        code:
          type: string
        textValue:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        numericValue:
          format: double
          nullable: true
          type: number
        dateValue:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        extendedTextValue:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        optionValues:
          items:
            type: string
          nullable: true
          type: array
        contactIds:
          items:
            format: uuid
            type: string
          nullable: true
          type: array
      required:
      - code
      type: object
    CreateCustomSymbolDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        country: country
        code: code
        formattedAddress: formattedAddress
        customFieldValues:
        - dateValue: dateValue
          code: code
          textValue: textValue
          numericValue: 0.8008281904610115
          extendedTextValue: extendedTextValue
          contactIds:
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          optionValues:
          - optionValues
          - optionValues
        - dateValue: dateValue
          code: code
          textValue: textValue
          numericValue: 0.8008281904610115
          extendedTextValue: extendedTextValue
          contactIds:
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          optionValues:
          - optionValues
          - optionValues
        city: city
        postalCode: postalCode
        name: name
        description: description
        stateProvince: stateProvince
        typeId: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        subTypeId: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        googleMapsPlaceId: googleMapsPlaceId
      properties:
        code:
          maxLength: 32
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        name:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        description:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        typeId:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        subTypeId:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        googleMapsPlaceId:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        formattedAddress:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        city:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        stateProvince:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        postalCode:
          maxLength: 10
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        country:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        customFieldValues:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolCustomFieldValueDto'
          nullable: true
          type: array
      type: object
    CreateStandardSymbolMetadataDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        country: country
        standardSymbol: standardSymbol
        formattedAddress: formattedAddress
        customFieldValues:
        - dateValue: dateValue
          code: code
          textValue: textValue
          numericValue: 0.8008281904610115
          extendedTextValue: extendedTextValue
          contactIds:
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          optionValues:
          - optionValues
          - optionValues
        - dateValue: dateValue
          code: code
          textValue: textValue
          numericValue: 0.8008281904610115
          extendedTextValue: extendedTextValue
          contactIds:
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          - 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
          optionValues:
          - optionValues
          - optionValues
        city: city
        postalCode: postalCode
        description: description
        stateProvince: stateProvince
        typeId: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        subTypeId: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        googleMapsPlaceId: googleMapsPlaceId
      properties:
        standardSymbol:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          type: string
        description:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        typeId:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        subTypeId:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        googleMapsPlaceId:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        formattedAddress:
          maxLength: 255
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        city:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        stateProvince:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        postalCode:
          maxLength: 10
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        country:
          maxLength: 50
          minLength: 0
          nullable: true
          type: string
        customFieldValues:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateCustomSymbolCustomFieldValueDto'
          nullable: true
          type: array
      required:
      - standardSymbol
      type: object
    CustomSymbolAddressDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        country: country
        formattedAddress: formattedAddress
        city: city
        postalCode: postalCode
        stateProvince: stateProvince
        googleMapsPlaceId: googleMapsPlaceId
      properties:
        googleMapsPlaceId:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        formattedAddress:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        city:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        stateProvince:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        postalCode:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        country:
          nullable: true
          type: string
      type: object
    CustomSymbolContact:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        isDeleted: true
        name: name
        roleName: roleName
        irnPersonId: irnPersonId
        employerName: employerName
        id: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
      properties:
        id:
          format: uuid
          type: string
        name:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        employerName:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        roleName:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        isDeleted:
          type: boolean
        irnPersonId:
          nullable: true
          type: string
      type: object
    CustomSymbolCustomFieldValueDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        code: code
        value: value
        contacts:
        - isDeleted: true
          name: name
          roleName: roleName
          irnPersonId: irnPersonId
          employerName: employerName
          id: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        - isDeleted: true
          name: name
          roleName: roleName
          irnPersonId: irnPersonId
          employerName: employerName
          id: 046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91
        optionValues:
        - optionValues
        - optionValues
      properties:
        code:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        value:
          nullable: true
          type: string
        optionValues:
          items:
            type: string
          nullable: true
          type: array
        contacts:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/CustomSymbolContact'
          nullable: true
          type: array
      type: object
    CustomSymbolDto:
      additionalProperties: false
      example:
        standardSymbolInstrumentData:
          tickerExchange: tickerExchange
          symbol: symbol
          cusip: cusip
          instrumentName: instrumentName
          identifiers:
          - identifiers
          - identifiers
          tickerRegion: tickerRegion
